      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey so im on warfarin right now for my heart and im taking 5mg every day. im feeling really good lately, no issues at all. i was thinking if i just dropped it down to like 2mg half the time i could still stay on it but more naturally? feels like too much medicine if i feel fine.",
